@host = http://localhost:8000

### Create question
POST {{host}}/v1/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "How do I borrow a value in Rust?#2",
  "body": "I keep getting a borrow checker error when I try to use a value after moving it. What is the idiomatic way to share a value without taking ownership?"
}

### Create question (invalid: empty title)
POST {{host}}/v1/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "body": "This request should fail validation because the title is empty."
}

### Create question (invalid: empty body)
POST {{host}}/v1/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "A valid title",
  "body": ""
}

### List questions
GET {{host}}/v1/questions?limit=10&offset=0
Accept: application/json

### Delete question
DELETE {{host}}/v1/questions/123x
Accept: application/json
